    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Martin Danielsson</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:234px;\"><a href=\"http://aigames.net/ACCA/ACCAWCRCC/2019ACCAWCRCC/martin_danielsson.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/39/Martin_danielsson.jpg\" width=\"232\" height=\"303\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Martin_danielsson.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Martin Danielsson <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Martin Danielsson</b>,<br />\na Swedish electrical engineer, M.Sc. from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lund_University\">Lund University</a> in 1999 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and as computer chess programmer author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Marvin\" title=\"Marvin\">Marvin</a>, originally developed in the early 2000s until 2005, \nfirst released in May 2004 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \nAfter ten years \"out of business\", Martin Danielsson restarted the development in 2015 - the completely rewritten Marvin <b>2.0.0</b> was released as <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source engine</a> under the terms of the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GNU General Public License</a> (GPL3) in March 2017 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2004_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2017_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Danielsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004_...\">2004 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Danielsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2004 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47529&amp;p=179735\">Marvin - new Winboard engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 09, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=1212&amp;p=5492\">Marvin 1.3.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 01, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=1460&amp;start=1\">Re: Command line tool to play engine matches</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 26, 2005</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017_...\">2017 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Danielsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2017 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63518\">Marvin 2.0.0 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 21, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66555\">Marvin 3.0.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 10, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71240\">Marvin 3.4.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Danielsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=74921\">Marvin 4.0.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 29, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_19\" title=\"TCEC Season 19\">TCEC Season 19</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76290\">Marvin 5.0.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Danielsson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Danielsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/martin-danielsson-297a703/\">Martin Danielsson | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/bmdanielsson\">bmdanielsson (Martin Danielsson) · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/bmdanielsson/marvin-chess\">GitHub - bmdanielsson/marvin-chess: Marvin - An UCI/XBoard compatible chess engine</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/bmdanielsson/nnue-trainer\">GitHub - bmdanielsson/nnue-trainer: PyTorch trainer for NNUE style neural networks</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?tit